cu.explanation_en: Setting the S1U port to 99999 exceeds the maximum allowed port number, causing configuration validation error.

du.explanation_en: Setting the uplink frequency band to 1000 exceeds the maximum allowed value, causing configuration validation error.
du.explanation_zh: 將上行頻率帶設定為 1000 超過最大允許值，會導致配置驗證錯誤。
